{"tid":1565431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中央政法委批評李嘉誠縱容犯罪","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:09:51.000Z","uid":14918,"like":21,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7badba94a33ac0319350b8d7e2da9f4912f26534","tid":1565431,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:53:07.000Z","msg":"長和資深顧問李嘉誠日前表示，政府應該對未來的主人翁網開一面。中央政法委在微博公眾號貼文，批評李嘉誠縱容犯罪，不是為香港著想，而是看著香港滑向深淵。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，在目前的香港亂局中，不少年輕人將樓價高、租金貴的憤怒，發洩到政府的頭上，但認為他們可能搞錯了發洩對象，又強調香港並不是沒有地，但發展總會遇到反對聲音，香港樓宇的天價對誰人有利，答案不難猜測，反問李嘉誠等「囤地圈錢」的地產商，會否對市民及香港的未來網開一面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480369-20190913.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480369-20190913.htm&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4Qcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=5376eccf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480369-20190913.htm&h=a7091bc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480369-20190913.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1e9d7001df87e3a100274c92c4e70c95303a102c","tid":1565431,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12dbc14166ef632fe208c5d888179d2933b0999","tid":1565431,"uid":14918,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"中共既鐵拳係咪要揮向地產霸權啦?"},{"pid":"3c14902bc76a1d41d19668a15d2716e5e2e5a7f1","tid":1565431,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:56:00.000Z","msg":"誠仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382da7c00869ff049ebc5ea73b1df08d23438cfe","tid":1565431,"uid":92734,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b12dbc14166e